<p><strong>Tale: Doctor Isabel Helga Anastasia Parvati Wondertainment, V is Displeased With Her Happy Meal</strong><br />
<strong>Authors:</strong> Team Crashing into Your DMs (<span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/devonmartin" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(1985558); return false;"><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=1985558&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1609721470" alt="devonmartin" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=1985558)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/devonmartin" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(1985558); return false;">devonmartin</a></span> and <span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/crashington" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(5028224); return false;"><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=5028224&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1609721470" alt="Crashington" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=5028224)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/crashington" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(5028224); return false;">Crashington</a></span>)</p>
